stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (HOW THIS PLANNER WORKS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Traditional schedules expect you to be a robot. You're not a robot.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (This planner uses ENERGY-BASED time blocking:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- Schedule hard tasks when your brain is ON) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- Protect low-energy times for easy wins) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- Build in buffer time \(because ADHD time blindness is real\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (- Only 3 priorities per day \(not 20\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (- Grace gaps between blocks for transitions) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
